      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, im T1D and my blood sugar is sitting at 185 right now. i want to get it back down to like 100 ASAP before dinner. i usually do a corrective bolus but i forgot what my sensitivity factor was. can u help me figure out how many units i should take to hit 100 right now? im a bit of a math person so just give me the calculation.",
